  m_text: "A Boiler is a closed vessel in which a  suitable liquid is heated to generate
    steam or vapour. The steam/vapour is then exited and is used for various purposes
    like heating applications such as water heating, central heating, it is also
    used for  boiler based power generation or even for cooking and various other
    purposes which could be domestic or industrial. \r\n\r\n"
